public void Startup() {
Gui Startupp = new Gui();
Startupp.setDefaultCloseOperation(JFrame.EXIT_ON_CLOSE); //How it closes
Startupp.setSize(450, 75); //The size, adjust the numbers to make bigger/smaller

Im using a 517 btw[/quote]
